{"tid":2020121,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想同所有想揾返ex/同ex復合嘅人講幾句","createTime":"2020-05-16T19:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T07:08:35.000Z","uid":320691,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a72590a86b916a3e1e1a43560dd0db2b3fd474","tid":2020121,"uid":320691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:40:59.000Z","msg":"係你做呢個決定前你真係要好好諗清楚夠竟係咪值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲人成日話咩人會變月會圓，但其實人有啲位根本係唔會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地上次因爲呢個問題而分手，就算你之後再揾返佢，個問題一樣會存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你只會再俾佢傷多次<br />\n<br />\n同埋千奇唔好因爲掛住以前嘅回憶而去揾返ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過左去嘅野係冇辦法再重現，就算你依加揾返佢，所有野都已經唔同曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然總有例外嘅，有啲人經歷過一次離合反而個情況會好左，但有幾多個人嘅結果真係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我同你地講，揾返ex係冇問題，但揾返佢之前真係要考慮清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好因一時衝動而令自己後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c119037bab10969b305b9d6b4b0d89901934712","tid":2020121,"uid":285339,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7a72590a86b916a3e1e1a43560dd0db2b3fd474","tid":2020121,"uid":320691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:40:59.000Z","msg":"係你做呢個決定前你真係要好好諗清楚夠竟係咪值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲人成日話咩人會變月會圓，但其實人有啲位根本係唔會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地上次因爲呢個問題而分手，就算你之後再揾返佢，個問題一樣會存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你只會再俾佢傷多次<br />\n<br />\n同埋千奇唔好因爲掛住以前嘅回憶而去揾返ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過左去嘅野係冇辦法再重現，就算你依加揾返佢，所有野都已經唔同曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"